UKCarGlass – Website Setup (BEST PRACTICE / v1.2)\par
\par
Purpose\par
Build ukcarglass.co.uk as a mobile-first UK booking platform that dispatches vetted mobile technicians to the customer’s address.\par
No branches. No local addresses. No location phone numbers. No “near me” city landing pages unless explicitly approved.\par
\par
Non‑negotiables\par
- Glass type is selected first (Windscreen / Rear / Side) before any long forms.\par
- Registration is the primary vehicle identifier. VIN is fallback.\par
- Never guess silently. Always confirm vehicle if confidence is low.\par
- Show a price estimate BEFORE showing the calendar.\par
- Side windows are supported in the flow but not promoted as a marketing topic.\par
- One primary CTA per page: “Get price and book”.\par
\par
