\par
Booking Flow (single /book route)\par
Route: /book with URL-synced state /book?step=1..7\par
\par
Step 1: Select glass position\par
- Options: Windscreen / Rear / Side\par
\par
Step 2: Enter registration number\par
- Validate format; allow “I don’t have it” fallback to manual make/model/year.\par
\par
Step 3: Resolve vehicle + explicit confirmation\par
- Backend: reg -> VIN -> vehicle profile\par
- Display: Make / Model / Year / Body type (+ note if uncertain)\par
- Require user confirmation.\par
\par
Step 4: Glass refinements (progressive disclosure)\par
- ADAS presence question (with tooltip + examples)\par
- Side window branch visual selector:\par
  - Left/Right, Front/Rear, Fixed/Vent/Drop, plus “Not sure”\par
- If ambiguity remains: ask one clarifying question, then allow “manual review”.\par
\par
Step 5: Quote summary (must be before calendar)\par
- Show: estimated price range + “what’s included” + warranty + ADAS note\par
- Toggle: insurance vs private\par
- CTA: Continue to availability\par
\par
Step 6: Choose date/time window\par
- Simple availability grid\par
\par
Step 7: Details + address + confirmation\par
- Name, phone, email\par
- Service address + notes\par
- Final CTA: “Pay & confirm booking” (Stripe Checkout)\par
\par
Confirmation: /book/confirmed\par
- Show booking reference, next steps, support, reschedule link.\par
\par
Payments (Stripe Checkout – required)\par
- Payment happens after quote + slot + address, before final confirmation.\par
- Create a Stripe Checkout Session server-side; redirect user; return to /book/confirmed.\par
\par
Server requirements:\par
- createCheckoutSession(bookingDraftId) -> \{ url \}\par
- webhook handler:\par
  - checkout.session.completed -> mark booking as paid, store payment_intent/session_id\par
  - checkout.session.expired -> keep draft, allow retry\par
\par
Config flags (env)\par
- PAYMENT_MODE = pay_now | deposit | pay_later (default pay_now)\par
\par
Tech Stack (recommended)\par
- Next.js (App Router) + TypeScript + Tailwind\par
- Supabase (Postgres) for storage; auth optional\par
- Stripe for payments\par
\par
Data Model (minimal)\par
vehicles, quotes, booking_drafts, bookings, payments, coverage_rules (see code comments)\par
\par
API / Server Actions (contract)\par
- resolveVehicle(reg)\par
- getCoverage(postcode)\par
- createQuote(payload)\par
- createBookingDraft(payload)\par
- createCheckoutSession(booking_draft_id)\par
- stripeWebhook(event)\par
\par
Noindex / indexing rules (must implement)\par
- /book?step=* -> NOINDEX, FOLLOW\par
- /book/confirmed -> NOINDEX, FOLLOW\par
- Vehicles default NOINDEX until page_quality >= 70\par
- No thin location/city pages\par
- Side-window informational pages -> NOINDEX, FOLLOW\par

